355176844137770", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75514543_355176847471103_340882097324378907_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=plD-60wTb6sQ7kNvgE8tiDm&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCICR--QAhLrCQR0tosTtxLeE2Jh0Zd0K6UMwzSh5hVZg&oe=674F046A"}, {"file_name": "tss1.png", "id": "2524319274394316", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75196218_2524319277727649_4669494071344934750_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6HmkOrRkuVYQ7kNvgEhi_Th&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAUpHUt8lDUBcGZ4p_1HNERYmXmX94QCcDMqiVnryshKg&oe=674EEBDA"}, {"file_name": "tss5.png", "id": "760707645548237", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974746_760707648881570_1069192667380168075_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IhbHuaVKLowQ7kNvgGNsW9h&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAgt5jkd_4J8Lu_x1sXmulz732zJqsKxso8L7hP9LQgKw&oe=674EDBAD"}, {"file_name": "s21.png", "id": "541147128406262", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75221322_541147131739595_7049747370601371318_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zcjtCvAVnwYQ7kNvgHrqK7c&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAwE2SCzRFriJF-y4KUFk2sh3-ds5PuZwQQfICjB_2DUw&oe=674EE0EF"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "thanks.png", "id": "575600448276122", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75250457_575600451609455_899177529865072388_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LCc6pzRRx2MQ7kNvgG-aZPY&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYARE7todz1lIeuF6YJOZqZvw-IuU0hmjaizrLFp5JCv0A&oe=674EF1C1"}, "display_name": "Monkey Doo", "keywords": ["free", "multiplayer", "physics", "gorilla", "action"], "long_description": "# \ud83e\udd83\ud83c\udf42Thanksgiving Update! \n\n- Thanksgiving Battle Pass and a brand new Mega Thanksgiving Bundle!\n- All-new food cosmetics \n- Lobby has a new autumn theme\n\n==================================================\n{2003598633407919}\n**About**\n# Live in the heart of the Bermuda Triangle with all your Monkey friends! Swing on vines, throw doo at your enemies, and climb everything! \n\n- Huge Maps: Explore the Bermuda Jungle, Floating Forests, Ancient Ruins, Lava Chasm, and more\n\n- Unique Gamemodes: Be the first to collect 10 bananas or work together to fend off hordes of crocs -- new modes are coming all the time\n\n- Monkey Apparel: Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo\n\n- Ruby Mines: Explore a seemingly endless set of tunnels filled with lore, new NPC's, and our Battle Pass! Unlock exclusive rewards like Cosmetics, Doos, Boosters, and more with free and paid rewards! \n\nThemed Cosmetics & Hands-on Fun: Get your hands on... well, new Hand cosmetics! Plus, a bunch of wacky, interactive items like things you can eat, press, and shake to your heart's content.\n\nHidden Treasures: Dive into a revamped store experience and hunt for secrets - like a mysterious portal leading to a hidden market. Plus, uncover new secrets via the plane!\n\nJump into the recently installed mining elevator to descend deep into the old ruby mines. Survive the **wrath of Xongo & save the Lost Souls** in Monkey Doo's all new Horror Mode!\n\n{872585647855554}\n\n", "short_description": "\ud83e\udd83\ud83c\udf42Thanksgiving Update! \n\nLive in the heart of the Bermuda Triangle with all your Monkey friends! Swing on vines, throw doo at your enemies, and climb everything! \n\n- Huge Maps: Explore the Bermuda Jungle, Floating Forests, Ancient Ruins, Lava Chasm, and more\n\n- Unique Gamemodes: Be the first to collect 10 bananas or explore the lost mines and save souls -- new modes are coming all the time!\n\n- Monkey Apparel: Customize your body color, equip face & head cosmetics, and stylize your doo"}]}, "developer_name": "Continuum XR", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://